export abstract class ButtonVariant {
    static readonly elevated = 'elevated'
    static readonly filled = 'filled'
    static readonly filledTonal = 'filled-tonal'
    static readonly outlined = 'outlined'
    static readonly text = 'text'
    static readonly icon = 'icon'
    static readonly segmented = 'segmented'
    static readonly fab = 'fab'
    static readonly extendedFab = 'extended-fab'
}

export abstract class RoundedVariant {
    static readonly none = 'none'
    static readonly sm = 'sm'
    static readonly md = 'md'
    static readonly lg = 'lg'
    static readonly full = 'full'
}
